sequenceDiagram
    participant App as Application
    participant API as API Gateway
    participant Lambda as Query Lambda
    participant Neptune as Neptune

    App->>API: Graph query request
    API->>Lambda: Invoke function
    Lambda->>Neptune: Execute Gremlin/SPARQL
    Neptune->>Neptune: Traverse graph
    Neptune-->>Lambda: Return results
    Lambda-->>API: Format response
    API-->>App: JSON results
